# VHS documentation
# https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs#installation

Output agents_tool_calls.mp4

Require opencode

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 28
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set TypingSpeed 140ms

Hide
Type "opencode"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Show

Type "Use a tool to look up the latest ECB inflation forecast and return one source URL."
Enter
Sleep 30s
